 ('2', '2', 'cs', 'Katalog technických řešení', '<p>It’s true, this site doesn’t have a whole lot of content yet, but don’t worry. Our web developers have just installed the CMS, and they’re setting things up for the content editors this very moment. Soon Koma-katalog.dev will be an oasis of fresh perspectives, sharp analyses, and astute opinions that will keep you coming back again and again.</p>', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-02-01 15:21:44', '2016-02-09 14:34:34', 'af15b1b8-073f-4359-9435-e4f381a78ae7'),
 ('3', '3', 'cs', 'We just installed Craft!', '<p>Craft is the CMS that’s powering Koma-katalog.dev. It’s beautiful, powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use, and it’s made by Pixel &amp; Tonic. We can’t wait to dive in and see what it’s capable of!</p><!--pagebreak--><p>This is even more captivating content, which you couldn’t see on the News index page because it was entered after a Page Break, and the News index template only likes to show the content on the first page.</p><p>Craft: a nice alternative to Word, if you’re making a website.</p>', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-02-01 15:21:44', '2016-02-02 12:18:11', '40c5663b-f922-439d-9993-1f3070e6ef17'),
